# My-Research.ai Project Overview

My-Research.ai is a specialized Knowledge Assistant Chatbot for professionals with citation support and credit-based subscription model.

The application uses:
- Next.js 15 with App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS with Shadcn UI
- Clerk for authentication
- Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL (Supabase)
- Pinecone Assistant API for knowledge retrieval
- Vercel Blob Storage for PDF storage

